ATM Machine m kya kya hota h

Card
Account


Initially ATM machine is in IDLE STATE
User will insert the card
Set is as the current card
Next State is HASCARDSTATE
Here you will validate the pin
If Pin is validated then you will advance to the next sstep that is SELECT Operationn
There are two type of operation supported i.e. WITHRAW AND CHECK BALANCE
Set the current Operation State
Then move to the next step that is perform the operation i.e. Tranasaction State
Then return the card --- IDLE STATE


STATES of ATM Machine

IDLE --  HASCARD -- SELECTOPERATION -- Tranasaction -- IDLE



There will be ATM Machine inventory also that will actually keeep the Actual Money
